Tips from ACloud Guru Serverless Approach:
==========================================

* No Ops? Yes Ops
* Don't look for serverless developers
* Encourage & Reassuring candidates
* Join the community
* Expect to Pioneer
* Serverless Monolith (Monolith to Microservices)
* Serverless amplifies the need for good developers practices
* Automation is not optional
* Test all the things (Test Driven Development)
* Managed services are moving targets

* Monoliths => Microservices => Serverless



